means: 容易征服的，易于克服的

sentence.Network_en: I am the best! I am the greatest! am in vincible!
sentence.Network_cn: 我是最好的! 我是最伟大的! 我是不可征服的!

sentence.Network_en: Most ignorance is vincible ignorance, We don't know because we don't want to now.
sentence.Network_cn: 许多疏漏是可以克服的, 只是因为我们不想知道怎么去做.
